title: Neha Dhupia to be the face of a fashion week in London
text:
Clotheshorse Neha Dhupia is now doing what she loves to do best â€” dress up.

Neha Dhupia 
The actress has been chosen as the face of a fashion week in London which celebrates Indian designers.
The event from October 9 to 12 will see Neha walk the ramp on the opening night, and attend the shows. On her return to Mumbai, expect Neha to step out in some more impeccable outfits.
